{"tid":2057313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新屋嶺輪姦案]與[刑事檢控專員對犯法通訊辦職員發出豁免起訴書]一案有關","createTime":"2020-06-09T09:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:08:17.000Z","uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81f1c7e0a1fe5a4129d0efb446761e563f40219e","tid":2057313,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"簡單講<br />\n呢單案係警魔指示通訊辦職員做犯法野配合搜證<br />\n<br />\n而律政司<br />\n1表明唔告通訊辦職員,發出豁免起訴書<br />\n<br />\n2<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">律政司明知通訊辦職員犯法,已表明若受害人提出私人檢控告通訊辦職員,一定會濫權把案件終止</span><br />\n-----------------<br />\n呢單案係試水溫,下一步:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁卓然會發出豁免起訴書比新屋嶺輪姦案的警魔,照告女受害人暴動<br />\n成堆受害人係監倉咪再無威脅</span></span>"},{"pid":"03b7c3436dffbe0bc66264a136b4d95e644ba716","tid":2057313,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Q0TLuj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Q0TLuj.gif&h=011f1e18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gttJ7HF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgttJ7HF.jpg&h=d5df8ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLC3of1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLC3of1.jpg&h=046b2f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe7b403682d2221b1d2243c95cbfe920e5cf4f00","tid":2057313,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8770359714463c0a3decbd48f534ea0eff1f001","tid":2057313,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"有部分女仔有求診<br />\n班警畜怕滅口反而會導致ha的人主動公開事件<br />\n故刑事檢控專員梁卓然呢半年一直諗方法屈受害人坐監<br />\n<br />\n呢單豁免起訴書只係第一步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二步係就算受害人係法院投訴遭輪姦同水刑, ,班警魔係法院認埋都好,因為有doj豁免起訴書都無從追究</span>"},{"p